<div class="case-study-card">
    <div class="header success">
        <span class="type">Case Study: Successful Restoration</span>
        <h4>Ichkeul National Park</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Once listed as World Heritage in Danger, Ichkeul is a global success story. Coordinated water management reversed ecological collapse.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Salinity:</strong> Reduced from crisis levels of 73 g/L to a sustainable 10-30 g/L range.</li>
            <li><strong>Bird Populations:</strong> Recovered from a low of 50,000 to 90,000-300,000 in optimal years.</li>
            <li><strong>Key Intervention:</strong> Coordinated dam releases ensuring 80-120 million mÂ³ of annual freshwater inflow.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

